data.description: This adorable 3 bedroom 2 bath home with vinyl siding and stone accents is move in ready!  Enjoy your covered front porch or back porch in the evenings.  With an open concept the kitchen overlooks the living area and eat in kitchen.  Kitchen has pantry and farm sink.  Master suite has tray ceilings and master bath has double vanity, garden tub, and separate shower. Dog run behind back fence.  Call us for your personal tour!
